cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper is about semantic segmentation learning, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel annotation enrichment strategy using neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence) and natural language processing (cs.CL - Computation and Language) for data annotation. Finally, the experiments involve the use of image and video processing techniques (cs.MM - Multimedia).
